Per-adapter --lora-strength for the LoRA stack (multi-LoRA follow-up to
issue #66 / ADR-0028). Against brxs/stable-audio-3 @ 36ef97776ee12375edd67a830a1bb0056d65bad8
(the sa3-pin.json commit). `--lora-strength` becomes one value per --lora
adapter (a single value still broadcasts, so existing invocations are
unchanged), and the merge scales each adapter's delta by its own strength.

To land: `git apply -p1` in the fork checkout, commit, push to
brxs/stable-audio-3, then bump the commit in sa3-pin.json (the app's
model manager offers the update in-place). Leading text like this is
ignored by `git apply`.

